name: sarcasticboy
0:
”Alexa open sarcastic boy”
”Alexa, ask sarcastic boy to tell me a dad joke.”
”Alexa, tell sarcastic boy to tell me a Rajinikanth joke.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sarcastic boy
des: The skill will make you laugh. When using the skill, you can say "Dad", "Rajinikanth" or "Any" to move to the next joke, or say "Yes" when skill asks you "do you want to hear another joke".
